  "texts": [
    "• Specialized LLMs.",
    "We prompt GPT-5 [23], GPT-5-mini [23] as code writer, employ Qwen2.5-Coder-32B-Instruct [24] as another code writer, and leverage Qwen2.5-Math-72B [25], Qwen2.5-Math-7B [25] as specialized math models.",
    "• Generalist LLMs.",
    "We consider GPT-5, GPT-5-mini, Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct [26], and Qwen3-32B [27] as representative generalist models.",
    "BaselinesWe compare Orchestrator-8B produced by ToolOrchestra to baseline orchestrators constructed by prompting LLMs."
